            <para>
              <text>The item relating to the Education Lands Act 1949 in Schedule 10 is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">(RS Vol 6, p 237)</emphasis></amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">(1949 No 24)</emphasis></amend.in>.</text>
