            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">3</label>
            <para>
              <text>The item relating to the Official Information Act 1982 in Schedule 10 is amended by inserting <amend.in quote="1"><emphasis style="bold">(1982 No 156)</emphasis></amend.in> after <emphasis style="bold"><quote.in quote="1">1982</quote.in></emphasis>.</text>
